casebody.head_matter:
SAC AND FOX NATION OF OKLOHAMA, et al., petitioners,
v.
BOROUGH OF JIM THORPE, PENNSYLVANIA, et al.
No. 14-1419.
Supreme Court of the United States
Oct. 5, 2015.
Motion of Senator Ben Nighthorse Campbell, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted.
